{"tid":1999720,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得拍拖只係一個公式遊戲，開始悶 繼續拍拖唔知為乜？","createTime":"2020-05-03T11:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T05:25:00.000Z","uid":129445,"like":35,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7737e922891e7147cf843625ce6a636de02a7be7","tid":1999720,"uid":129445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:01:00.000Z","msg":"拍唔拍得成拖只係講兩樣野，條件同感覺。<br />\n<br />\n拍拖一開始只係講條件既遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n樣貌  身材  金錢  才能<br />\n<br />\n唔符合條件既人就開始唔到呢個game。"},{"pid":"c1bafc7835522d534640e2b148ce672b5fc738b2","tid":1999720,"uid":129445,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:03:52.000Z","msg":"第二 感覺<br />\n<br />\n好簡單，當你fulfill 到人地既條件 靠既只係你把口或者做下On9野就可以成功。<br />\n<br />\n當然首先你要達到人地條件先，不過條件未夠既都可以靠技巧 營造好既感覺就可以一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d74de4927c5950f46fa1487647e29e3c7b4054","tid":1999720,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52635e298aa18f97553ba04541f404cb32b3054c","tid":1999720,"uid":64838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:04:51.000Z","msg":"拍過幾多次拖同拍左幾耐呀？"},{"pid":"7b7b69da7ea8dec935db5d1292e4f166afe7c112","tid":1999720,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:05:20.000Z","msg":"1年1件<br />\n再耐少少就會悶"},{"pid":"292419e25a735ca1797cee0c390a532d73f3d4bf","tid":1999720,"uid":129445,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:06:19.000Z","msg":"其實拍拖真係唔難，當你識搵對手，識一定既技巧就可以一齊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b40ad340fcfe726747a90beaf687f0ed3a9962","tid":1999720,"uid":129445,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"52635e298aa18f97553ba04541f404cb32b3054c","tid":1999720,"uid":64838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:04:51.000Z","msg":"拍過幾多次拖同拍左幾耐呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:06:42.000Z","msg":"唔多 3次 最耐4年半"},{"pid":"c3f494c4c814d51dc6078ff59e4753d88ded4dca","tid":1999720,"uid":129445,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:12:13.000Z","msg":"雖然唔難，但我已經開始覺得悶。老老實實 你搵得既對象除非集郵或者想試新野，同理想中既唔會好大出入。<br />\n撇除身型 外貌唔講，但鍾意既性格都唔會話差太遠。但每一次新感情又要用同樣心機放落去，分分鐘又再次經歷同一個場境既時候。<br />\n我就好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81d649e19810dc98a9a82127faa8c5081519848","tid":1999720,"uid":129445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b7b69da7ea8dec935db5d1292e4f166afe7c112","tid":1999720,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:05:20.000Z","msg":"1年1件<br />\n再耐少少就會悶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:13:52.000Z","msg":"拍緊個陣我就唔會悶既，因為我就係覺得我鍾意既都係差唔多。就算宜家悶 對下一個都會悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53d7bc2b1576d7bad549079d0ff3d2ea1f1c46b","tid":1999720,"uid":63127,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:13:57.000Z","msg":"係咪因爲你地雙方冇一個共同目標/方向繼續落去"},{"pid":"0b7d8712c482ba5d662c7fe996b3451749390405","tid":1999720,"uid":23699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:14:11.000Z","msg":"肯定係講 package <br />\n港台個節目有眼你睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fff23b41929683809fb379a9adbf151cc918f63","tid":1999720,"uid":129445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e53d7bc2b1576d7bad549079d0ff3d2ea1f1c46b","tid":1999720,"uid":63127,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:13:57.000Z","msg":"係咪因爲你地雙方冇一個共同目標/方向繼續落去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:15:18.000Z","msg":"拍緊拖個陣，唔會悶呀。可以同另一半好好相處"},{"pid":"a5fa254655a428dd8efb827b5c3fe846eb4bbed9","tid":1999720,"uid":205125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"292419e25a735ca1797cee0c390a532d73f3d4bf","tid":1999720,"u